<field name="name">

&lt;P&gt;
link - create a hard link in the filesytem

&lt;P&gt;
&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
<field name="synopsis">

&lt;P&gt;
link 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;OLDFILE,NEWFILE&lt;/FONT&gt;

&lt;P&gt;
&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
<field name="description">

&lt;P&gt;
Creates a new filename linked to the old filename. Returns 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;TRUE&lt;/FONT&gt; for success, 
&lt;FONT SIZE=-1&gt;FALSE&lt;/FONT&gt; otherwise.

&lt;HR&gt;
</field>
